name: Paris Street - UE5
description:
I've been chipping away at this personal project over the summer break. I had saved this concept by Robin Lhebrard for a while and have been wanting to make more of a "city" environment so I thought it was the perfect time to give it a go. Somewhere along the way I migrated everything to UE5 because I wanted to check out lumen and see what else is new. I had a blast creating this and I might even if I find the time create a night version as well.
Hope you like it!
